thread.title: Peter, Ivanhoe
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Peter, Ivanhoe

author: Peter, Ivanhoe
title: Peter, Ivanhoe
text: I have bought a number of home recording studio items from StoreDJ because they have a great range of products, always competitive prices and deliver what I want, in good condition, quickly. I always check round the Net for comparative prices but often find myself back at StoreDJ for the best offer. No hesitation recommending that people look closely at what they offer.
